3 4.5. Criminal and civil penalties may not be imposed upon an individual for an action taken
4 in accordance with an opinion issued under this section if:
5 a. The individual acts in good faith; and
6 b. The material facts surrounding the action taken are substantially the same as the
7 conduct presented in the opinion.
8 5.6. Opinions and requests for opinions under this section are open records, except names
9 of persons in the opinions and requests are exempt records.
10 6.7. The ethics commission shall publish all written advisory opinions issued under this
11 section on a website that is accessible to the public.
